ystem</h3>                    <p>Flip Skater Idle introduces automated performance features. Once unlocked, your skater continues generating passive income even when you're not actively playing.</p>                    <p>Automation upgrades include:</p>                    <ul>                        <li>Auto-trick execution</li>                        <li>Passive sponsorship income</li>                        <li>Offline rewards multiplier</li>                    </ul>                    <p>This hybrid system balances active play with idle progression, similar to growth mechanics seen in Cookie Clicker, but adapted for a sports setting.</p>                    <h2>Scaling Strategy Guide</h2>                    <div class="content-section-table-wrap">                        <table class="content-table">                            <thead>                                <tr>                                    <th>Phase</th>                                    <th>Focus</th>                                    <th>Objective</th>                                </tr>                            </thead>                            <tbody>                                <tr>                                    <td>Early Game</td>                                    <td>Trick Consistency</td>                                    <td>Build stable income</td>                                </tr>                                <tr>                                    <td>Mid Game</td>                                    <td>Combo Multipliers</td>                                    <td>Increase profit per run</td>                                </tr>                                <tr>                                    <td>Late Game</td>                                    <td>Automation</td>                                    <td>Maximize passive earnings</td>                                </tr>                                <tr>                                    <td>End Game</td>    